tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE musicians (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
name VARCHAR,
birthdate DATE,
hometown VARCHAR);

CREATE TABLE albums (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
title VARCHAR,
release_date DATE,
artist_id INT,
FOREIGN KEY (artist_id) REFERENCES musicians(id));

CREATE TABLE albums (
  album_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  album_name VARCHAR(50),
  release_date DATE,
  musician_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (musician_id) REFERENCES musicians(musician_id)
);

CREATE TABLE tracks (
  track_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  track_name VARCHAR(50),
  duration TIME,
  album_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (album_id) REFERENCES albums(album_id)
);

CREATE TABLE albums (
  album_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  album_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  release_date DATE,
  musician_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (musician_id) REFERENCES musicians(musician_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Records (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    record_name VARCHAR,
    release_date DATE,
    artist_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (artist_id) REFERENCES Musicians(id)
);

CREATE TABLE Albums (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    album_name VARCHAR,
    release_year INT,
    band_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (band_id) REFERENCES Bands(id)
);

CREATE TABLE Songs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    song_name VARCHAR,
    duration INT,
    record_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (record_id) REFERENCES Records(id)
);
